verbose_text: Although R-spondins are expected to act through beta-catenin stabilization and may synergize with WNT proteins [XREF_BIBR], the survival analysis grouped by WNT1 expression suggests that RSPO1 exerts a protective effect through a pathway other than WNT1 signaling in invasive ductal cancer.
